id: pm-mzlu
title: "PR #123 review: make governance hook sidecar logging fail-open"
description: Follow-up to pm-7m8p from CodeRabbit/Gemini review. Make PM_GOVERNANCE_AUDIT_HOOK_LOG sidecar filesystem writes best-effort so permissions/ENOSPC/invalid path do not break core read/write hook flows; cache created directories; add regression coverage; rerun focused validation and retrigger review agents.
