author: codex-implementation
parent: pm-7m8p
resolution: Made optional governance hook sidecar logging best-effort so filesystem errors cannot interrupt core read/write hook flows.
expected_result: Invalid or unwritable sidecar paths do not throw from governance audit hooks; normal compact sidecar logging still works.
actual_result: "Hook helper wraps mkdir/append in try/catch, caches log directories, keeps compact records unchanged, and tests/smoke/coverage all passed."
